    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required levels. One factor (Test conditions) achieved level 2 against a required level of 3; this gap is accepted given the explicit scope limitation to static compression-bending and the existence of a separate fatigue COU. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-specified acceptance thresholds (E/uval < 1.96; percentage difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is judged credible for the stated COU. Note: aleatory uncertainty in the force-at-40-mm validation result was assessed qualitatively only; a structured UQ record was not produced for that result.",
